cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.CL

This paper discusses teaching a model by demonstration in a sequential decision making environment, which involves machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) techniques. The focus on the teacher as a decision maker suggests relevance to robotics (cs.RO) and control systems (cs.SY). The paper also mentions handling noise and sequences of inputs, which could involve natural language processing (cs.CL).
